headline: Hormel Foods (NYSE:HRL) Dividends Affirmed at US$0.29 as Shares Dip 2%
summary: Hormel Foods (NYSE:HRL) recently declared a quarterly dividend of $0.29 per share and launched a new product, FONTANINI Hot Honey Sliced Sausage, at the International Pizza Expo, aligning with consumer trends. Despite these developments, the company experienced a 1.32% decline in its share price over the past month.
